From: Dave Gerlach <d-gerlach@ti.com>
Date: Wed, 24 Jun 2015 13:34:37 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 196/800] ARM: dts: am33xx: Add sram phandle to soc node

Add a phandle to our sram node so that the pm code can locate the sram
to copy low level pm code.

Signed-off-by: Dave Gerlach <d-gerlach@ti.com>
[zou: Original patch taken from PROCESSOR-SDK-LINUX-AM335X 02_00_01_07]
Signed-off-by: zou cao <cao.zou@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/am33xx.dtsi |    1 +
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/am33xx.dtsi b/arch/arm/boot/dts/am33xx.dtsi
index 65c2a5d..f6c2577 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/am33xx.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/am33xx.dtsi
@@ -80,6 +80,7 @@
 		mpu {
 			compatible = "ti,omap3-mpu";
 			ti,hwmods = "mpu";
+			sram = <&ocmcram>;
 		};
 	};
 
